Interface PaAttributeValueRemediationParameterUriBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface PaAttributeValueRemediationParameterUriBuilder
extends PaAttributeSubValueBuilder<PaAttributeValueRemediationParameterUri>
    Generic builder to build an integrity measurement URI remediation parameter value compliant to RFC 5792. It can be used in a fluent way.
